Version 0.6.0 (2018-08-29)
--------------------------
Track page URL in the tracker subject (closes #92)
Add SyncBatchEmitter (closes #70)
Bump Iglu Scala Core to 0.3.0 (closes #101)
Introduce independent algebras for clock time and uuid (closes #99)
Improve code coverage (closes #98)
Release referentially transparent Metadata module separately (closes #96)
Release emitters separately (closes #46)
Make API referentially transparent (closes #74)
Replace json4s with circe (closes #71)
Remove deprecated trackUnstructEvent (closes #94)
Add compiler options (closes #93)
Extend copyright notices to 2018 (closes #89)
Bump sbt-bintray to 0.5.4 (closes #90)
Bump specs2 to 4.3.2 (closes #88)
Add support for codecov (#77)
Bump sbt to 1.2.0 (closes #87)
Replace release badge by a maven central badge (closes #79)
Add Gitter badge (closes #76)
Drop support for Scala 2.10 (closes #75)
Make Scala 2.12 the default version (closes #80)
Add issue template (closes #83)
Add pull request template (closes #84)
Add CONTRIBUTING.md (closes #85)
Integrate scalafmt (closes #86)
Remove vagrant setup (closes #73)
Remove cruft from .gitignore (closes #81)


